   nn
</P>
<P>
   ON TIES
</P>
<P>
   Q: You mentioned, obviously, that you've given the president
several gifts. Have you given him any ties? A: Yes.
</P>
<P>
   Q: How many ties have you given him, just approximately?
</P>
<P>
   A:Six.
