   DECK-CARE _ The deck is just another ``room'' of the house at
the Linthicum residence. Gary and Janet Linthicum of Woodway and
their four children spend hours outside ``living'' on their deck.
At 700 square feet it is larger than many small apartments. (Mays,
Waco Tribune-Herald) MOVED.
</P>
