<P>
   WINE-TALK (Undated) _ If you plan to buy wine in the next few
weeks, and you probably do, as more wine is sold in the fourth
quarter of the year than at any other time, there is no question
about what you should buy: 1995 Bordeaux. It is one of the better
vintages of the waning century. By Frank J. Prial.
</P>
