<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-09-22 17:59 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A8544 &Cx1f; taf-z
u f &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-CREDIT-NYT &LR;      09-22 0426
