   MA-TRIPLE-FATAL (Pembroke, Mass.) -- Three schoolgirls are
killed and another critically injured when their car hydroplanes on
a rain-slicked road and crashes into a pickup. The tragedy plunges
a small Catholic school into mourning. By Brian MacQuarrie. 1000
words.
