<HEADLINE>
BUSINESS TRAVEL: PHILIPPINE AIRLINES TO SHUT DOWN; HIGHER AIR FARES
EXPECTED; WORLD'S LARGEST PASSENGER SHIP 
</HEADLINE>
  (Also moved in ``f'' category.) 
(lb) 
 By EDWIN McDOWELL   
 c.1998 N.Y. Times News Service   
<TEXT>
